des: Bikes To Boards is a cool Platform for Skateboard and BMX riders that love the culture of Bikes and Boards. As we all know skateboarding and bmx riding is a very fast growing sport in the USA and worldwide so we wanted to carve out a space we could dedicate to the sport to show our love and support for Bikes and Skateboards! The information in this skill is provided for informational and educational purposes only.
